'''Ciarán Hinds''' is an Irish actor. He portrayed the [[Dark Wizard]] in the second season of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]'' series by [[Amazon Studios]].<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://press.amazonstudios.com/us/en/press-release/ciaran-hinds-rory-kinnear-and-tanya-moodie-join-ca|articlename=Ciarán Hinds, Rory Kinnear, and Tanya Moodie Join Cast of Prime Video’s The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power for Season Two|dated=|website=AmazonMGMStudios|accessed=14 April 2024}}</ref>
